The Adventures of Scott and ...

Welcome to the Adventures of Scott and... - I am a motovlogger, a race car driver, and a complete knucklehead. You'll find me on the weekends riding my sport bike, supermoto, dual-sport, or race car. I have a girlfriend...and she's into the exact same stuff. I like to record my adventures and share on YouTube!

item.title: Nearly Crashed on Mulholland Snake
item.description:
Nearly Crashed on Mulholland Snake
